title: Daffy Qaddafi (1986)
description:
Anonymously credited U.S. agitprop where it's alluded Qaddafi has sex with livestock, is jackshit insane, and attends a "Tea Party" with Ronald Reagan. 
Featuring Tattoo from Fantasy Island, and Daffy Duck.


DAFFY QADDAFI: MALICE IN WONDERLAND 
1986 comic book, credited to "Comics USA". Beautiful nonsense. No information on artist and writer, and is the only comic to have been produced by company ... and despite weird presentation is quite researched and specific.

Issued during peak of rivalry between Gaddafi and Reagan, or as the burlesque song title from 1955 says "We're Stuck Between Those Two Assholes (again)"
